---
title: How to add  a youtube live stream option in lesson videos? 
show_child_cards: true
excerpt: Learn How to add  a youtube live stream option in lesson videos.
---

In order to add the YouTube live stream option to the lesson videos, please follow the steps below to do so.

- Go to  Masteriyo > Courses 
- Click on Edit or Add new Course 
- Navigate to builder and add new lesson.
- For the **Video Source** dropdown option, please select the **Live Stream** option.
![youtube-live-stream-option](https://github.com/Masteriyo/masteriyo-docs/assets/90859959/3fa511d7-8363-42f4-a985-47fa3ee6aac4)
